      "designInstructions": "## Aurora — Modern Mobile-First Design Language\n\nA vibrant, joyful productivity app aesthetic. The primary violet energy signals innovation and clarity. Mobile-first, touch-optimized, generous whitespace, with an elevated sense of craft at every pixel.\n\n### Color\nPrimary: deep violet `#7c3aed`. Background: `#f5f3ff` — a barely-perceptible violet wash that unifies the page. Cards are pure white on this backdrop, creating layered depth. The gradient hero uses `linear-gradient(135deg, #6d28d9, #4338ca)` — a rich indigo depth. Colored icon boxes (green `#d1fae5`, amber `#fef3c7`, red `#fee2e2`, violet `#ede9fe`) act as visual tags for each stat type.\n\n### Typography\n**Plus Jakarta Sans** exclusively. H1/hero: 800 weight, -0.02em tracking. Section labels: 700. Body: 500/400. The large KPI numbers display at 1.4–1.6rem with 800 weight and tight letter-spacing, creating punchy visual impact at thumb distance.\n\n### Mobile Components\n**Hero gradient card**: full-width, `border-radius: 20px`, gradient background, white text. Contains main stats inline. Decorative soft-circle ornaments in bottom-right corner at rgba(255,255,255,0.06).\n**Stat grid**: 2×2 grid of white cards, 16px radius, `box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(124,58,237,0.07)`. Each card has a 36×36 colored icon box (10px radius) and a large bold number.\n**Crop cards**: horizontal flex rows with emoji icon box (46×46, 13px radius, colored bg), text stack + mini progress bar, status pill. Shadow: `0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.04)`.\n**Progress bars**: 4px height, gradient fills matching status color, `border-radius: 99px`.\n**Status pills**: `border-radius: 99px`, 0.65rem, weight 700, color-matched to status.\n**Bottom navigation**: white, `border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb`, 5 tabs. Active tab has a colored rounded-square bg (40×36px, 10px radius, muted-color fill) + colored label. Inactive tabs: 55% opacity.\n\n### Transitions\nAll 200ms `ease-out`. Card hover: `box-shadow` grows — no transform. Button: background shifts one step darker.\n",
      "created": "2026-05-31T01:59:09.029217+00:00",
      "modified": "2026-05-31T02:17:13.455641+00:00"
    },
