      "designInstructions": "## Obsidian — Dark Modern Mobile Design Language\n\nA sleek professional dark-mode app for agronomists working early mornings and late evenings. The deep space backgrounds make data glow, stats breathe, and alerts feel urgent. Think Raycast meets precision agriculture.\n\n### Color Philosophy\nThree dark surface tiers define depth without borders: `#0a0f1a` (void/page), `#131929` (card/nav), `#1a2332` (elevated/KPI chip). The primary emerald `#34d399` is vivid but not garish — it's the green of growth sensors in the dark. Borders are `#1f2937` — just barely visible, drawing structure without weight. Status colors: amber `#fbbf24`, red `#f87171`, cyan `#22d3ee`.\n\n### Typography\n**Outfit** throughout — a geometric humanist sans that reads beautifully in white on dark, with natural round strokes that feel warm not cold. Headings 700–800, body 400–500. KPI numbers display at 1.2rem, 700 weight, in primary green.\n\n### Mobile Components\n**Header**: `#131929` bg, dark avatar with green gradient `#34d399→#059669`, monogram in `#052e16`.\n**Glass summary card**: `rgba(26,35,50,0.9)` bg, `border: 1px solid rgba(52,211,153,0.15)`, `border-radius: 20px`. Large radial gradient glow in top-right corner at 8% opacity. 3-column stats grid.\n**KPI scroll chips**: horizontal `overflow-x: auto`, flex chips. Each `#1a2332` bg, `#2d3748` border, 12px radius. Values in brand colors.\n**Chart**: Chart.js bar chart at fixed 140px height. Bars with emerald gradient opacity (50%→100% left to right). Dark bg, minimal gridlines `rgba(45,55,72,0.3)`, Outfit font ticks.\n**Crop cards**: `#131929` bg, `#1f2937` border, 16px radius. Glow border on alert cards `rgba(248,113,113,0.2)`. Progress bars 3px, brand-colored fills. Status badges: `rgba(color,0.1)` bg + `rgba(color,0.25)` border + color text.\n**Bottom nav**: `#131929` bg, `#1f2937` top border. Active: `rgba(52,211,153,0.1)` bg + emerald border + emerald label. Inactive: 45% opacity.\n\n### Data Visualization\nBar chart bars use progressive emerald opacity `rgba(52,211,153, 0.5→1.0)` across months — builds anticipation left-to-right. `borderRadius: 6` on bars. Tooltip: `#1a2332` bg, emerald title.\n",
      "created": "2026-05-31T01:59:40.966710+00:00",
      "modified": "2026-05-31T02:17:33.565550+00:00"
    },
