      "designInstructions": "## Meadow — Clean Modern Green Mobile Design Language\n\nA fresh, trustworthy design language grounded in the green-and-white familiarity of modern productivity apps. Feels like a well-designed banking app or health tracker — approachable, clean, instantly legible. The green signals growth without being heavy.\n\n### Color\nPure white `#ffffff` background. Primary: `#16a34a` (green-600) — confident, natural. Accent: `#f0fdf4` for all tinted surfaces. The hero card is a rich emerald gradient `#16a34a → #059669 → #047857`. Card borders: `#e5e7eb` (cool neutral). Alert red: `#ef4444`. Surveillance amber: `#d97706`. All color used at 100% saturation — no muted palettes, clean and direct.\n\n### Typography\n**Inter** at every weight. Headings: 800 at -0.02em. Section titles: 800. Body: 500–600 for readability at small mobile sizes. KPI numbers: 1.25rem at 800 weight. No display serifs — this is a lean, precise aesthetic.\n\n### Signature Design Element\n**Colored left-border on crop cards**: `border-left: 3px solid [status color]`, `border-radius: 0 14px 14px 0`. Green for healthy, amber for surveillance, red for alert. This is the visual encoding system — one glance tells the story of every field.\n\n### Mobile Components\n**Hero banner**: full-width gradient card, 20px radius. Stats displayed in a 3-column frosted row `rgba(255,255,255,0.15)` inside the card.\n**Quick action buttons**: 2-column grid. Primary: solid green fill, white text. Secondary: `#f0fdf4` fill with `#bbf7d0` border and green text.\n**Alert banner**: `#fef2f2` bg, `#fecaca` border, 14px radius. Flex with icon box + text + right chevron.\n**Crop cards**: White bg, left-border status encoding, `box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.04)`. Progress bars 4px with gradient fills. Status pills: `border-radius: 99px`, filled with muted color bg, 1px solid border.\n**Bottom nav**: White, `border-top: 1.5px solid #f0fdf4`. Active tab has `#f0fdf4` bg + `#bbf7d0` border. Inactive: 45% opacity.\n\n### UX Focus\nLarge 44px+ touch targets. Clear visual hierarchy at glance distance. Every piece of data at a farm-critical size. Simple mental model: white = clean, green = good, amber = watch, red = act now.\n",
      "created": "2026-05-31T02:00:14.406415+00:00",
      "modified": "2026-05-31T02:17:51.594087+00:00"
